Choose exactly one tool:
- add_task
- add_reminder
- update_task
- update_reminder
- no_action

Guidelines:
- Use add_task when the item is a to-do or action.
- Use add_reminder for simple, quick reminders.
- Use update_task/update_reminder only when the item refers to an existing item.
- If unsure or no action needed, choose no_action.

For add_task:
- category must be one of the TaskCategory enum values (UPPERCASE).
- timing_type must be one of the TimingType enum values (UPPERCASE) if provided.
- time fields should be 24h format HH:MM.

For update_task:
- action must be "complete" or "punt".
